metadata.title: Cessna 206
aws::graph::propositions: Cessna 206 Aircraft Variants and Production History
Cessna 206 was certified on July 20, 1967.
420 total Cessna 206 aircraft were built in 1967.
320 U206C/TU206C variants of Cessna 206 were built.
100 P206C/TP206C variants of Cessna 206 were built.
U206D Skywagon 206 was introduced for the 1969 model year.
U206D Skywagon 206 featured minor changes from previous models.
U206D Skywagon 206 floatplane version had a larger fin and rudder.
U206D Skywagon 206 was also built in passenger P206D variant.
U206D Skywagon 206 was also built in turbocharged TU206D variant.
U206D Skywagon 206 was also built in turbocharged TP206D variant.
Utility variants of Cessna 206 were renamed as "Skywagon 206".
Passenger variants of Cessna 206 kept the "Super Skylane" name.
U206D Skywagon 206 was certified on September 18, 1968.
294 total U206D Skywagon 206 aircraft were built.
210 U206D/TU206D variants of Cessna 206 were built.
84 P206D/TP206D variants of Cessna 206 were built.
U206E Skywagon 206/Stationair was introduced for the 1970 model year.
U206E Skywagon 206/Stationair featured a redesigned cowling.
U206E Skywagon 206/Stationair included minor changes from previous models.
U206E Skywagon 206/Stationair was also built in passenger P206E variant.
U206E Skywagon 206/Stationair was also built in turbocharged TU206E variant.
U206E Skywagon 206/Stationair was also built in turbocharged TP206E variant.

text:
Certified on July 20, 1967.  420 total built; 320 (U206C/TU206C) and 100 (P206C/TP206C).
U206D Skywagon 206
1969 model year with minor changes, as well as a larger fin and rudder on the floatplane version.  Also built in passenger P206D and turbocharged TU206D and TP206D variants.  Utility variants were renamed as the "Skywagon 206", while the passenger variants kept the "Super Skylane" name.  Certified on September 18, 1968.  294 total built; 210 (U206D/TU206D) and 84 (P206D/TP206D).
U206E Skywagon 206/Stationair
Introduced for the 1970 model year with a redesigned cowling and minor changes.  Also built in passenger P206E and turbocharged TU206E and TP206E variants.
